tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE image_relationships (
    relationship_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    image_id UUID,
    label_id UUID,
    tag_id UUID,
    FOREIGN KEY (image_id) REFERENCES labeled_images(image_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (label_id) REFERENCES image_labels(label_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (tag_id) REFERENCES image_tags(tag_id)
);

CREATE TABLE image_metadata (
    metadata_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    image_id UUID REFERENCES labeled_images(image_id),
    label_id UUID REFERENCES image_labels(label_id),
    width INT,
    height INT,
    format VARCHAR(10)
);

CREATE TABLE training_data (
    data_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    image_id UUID REFERENCES labeled_images(image_id),
    label_id UUID REFERENCES image_labels(label_id),
    training_type VARCHAR(20),
    accuracy FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE neural_networks (
    network_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    network_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE,
    architecture TEXT,
    num_layers INT,
    training_data_id UUID REFERENCES training_data(data_id)
);
